Prerequisites:
Install QR Code Generator:
      Install the qrencode package, which is required for generating QR codes for UPI payments.
Use the following command:
        sudo apt-get install qrencode
Project Setup:
    Place all the project files (e.g., main.c, translation.c, translation.h, payment.h) in the same directory (e.g., my-projects).
    Open the payment.h file and enter your UPI ID where indicated.
Compilation:
          Navigate to the project directory in your terminal.
  Compile the project using the following command:
          g++ -std=c++20 main.cpp -lqrencode
Run the Program:
          If the compilation is successful, run the program by typing:   ./a.out
